you feel about specific aspects of your life.**"}, {"name": "wellbeing1", "path": "/survey/wellbeing/wellbeing1", "type": "string", "binary": null, "value_type": "select_one satisfaction", "hintenglish_en": null, "selectMultiple": null, "labelenglish_en": "**Thinking about your own life and personal circumstances, how satisfied are you with your life as a whole?**"}, {"name": "wellbeing2", "path": "/survey/wellbeing/wellbeing2", "type": "string", "binary": null, "value_type": "select_one satisfaction", "hintenglish_en": null, "selectMultiple": null, "labelenglish_en": "**How satisfied are you with your standard of living?**"}, {"name": "wellbeing3", "path": "/survey/wellbeing/wellbeing3", "type": "string", "binary": null, "value_type": "select_one satisfaction", "hintenglish_en": null, "selectMultiple": null, "labelenglish_en": "**How satisfied are you with your health?**"}, {"name": "wellbeing4", "path": "/survey/wellbeing/wellbeing4", "type": "string", "binary": null, "value_type": "select_one satisfaction", "hintenglish_en": null, "selectMultiple": null, "labelenglish_en": "**How satisfied are you with what you are achieving in life?**"}, {"name": "wellbeing5", "path": "/survey/wellbeing/wellbeing5", "type": "string", "binary": null, "value_type": "select_one satisfaction", "hintenglish_en": null, "selectMultiple": null, "labelenglish_en": "**How satisfied are you with your personal relationships?**"}, {"name": "wellbeing6", "path": "/survey/wellbeing/wellbeing6", "type": "string", "binary": null, "value_type": "select_one satisfaction", "hintenglish_en": "Meaning physical safety.", "selectMultiple": null, "labelenglish_en": "**How satisfied are you with how safe you feel?**"}, {"name": "wellbeing7", "path": "/survey/wellbeing/wellbeing7", "type": "string", "binary": null, "value_type": "select_one satisfaction", "hintenglish_en": "Meaning feeling of inclusivity, or sense of belongingness.", "selectMultiple": null, "labelenglish_en": "**How satisfied are you with