 have to make important decisions in the food system, for example about how and what kind of food is produced, where it goes, how much it costs, and how and what kind of food people consume. Please imagine a five-step ladder, where at the bottom on the first step stand individual men and women of the community with little capacity to make their own decisions about food production, trade or consumption. These individuals have little to say about types and varieties of crops, animals, trees, they produce, the way they manage their water, land, soil, animals, and wildlife, the markets available to them, and the food source and food choices available to them. On the highest step, the fifth, stand those who have great capacity to make important decisions for themselves, including what they grow, how they manage their land, soil, water, animals, and trees, who they sell the food to, and what food they buy.**"}, {"name": "hhwomen_agency_step_now", "path": "/survey/farmer_agency/hhwomen_agency_step_now", "type": "string", "binary": null, "value_type": "select_one step_power", "hintenglish_en": null, "selectMultiple": null, "labelenglish_en": "**On which step of the ladder would you position the majority of women in your household today?**"}, {"name": "agency_text1", "path": "/survey/farmer_agency/agency_text1", "type": "string", "binary": null, "value_type": "text", "hintenglish_en": null, "selectMultiple": null, "labelenglish_en": "**Could you explain the main reasons for your rating?**"}, {"name": "agency_audio1", "path": "/survey/farmer_agency/agency_audio1", "type": "binary", "binary": true, "value_type": "audio", "hintenglish_en": null, "selectMultiple": null, "labelenglish_en": "**Could you explain the main reasons for your rating?**"}, {"name": "hhwomen_agency_step_10yrs", "path": "/survey/farmer_agency/hhwomen_agency_step_10yrs", "type": "string", "binary": null, "value_type": "select_one step_power", "hintenglish_en": null, "selectMultiple": null, "labelenglish_en"